Email automation platforms are at the forefront of simplifying follow-up tasks. Tools such as Mailchimp, ActiveCampaign, or HubSpot not only allow for mass email campaigns but also enable personalized follow-ups based on user behavior. For instance, if a client opens your email but doesn’t respond, you can set up a trigger that automatically sends a tailored reminder after a specific timeframe.

